'''HIP 11915'''是一顆距離地球約186光年的[[黃矮星|黃矮星]]，在天球上位於[[鯨魚座|鯨魚座]]<ref name="Extrasolar">{{cite web |title=Planet HIP 11915 |url=http://exoplanet.eu/catalog/hip_11915/ |accessdate=17 July 2015 |archive-date=2015-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210235120/http://exoplanet.eu/catalog/hip_11915/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SIMBAD">{{cite web|title=Simbad Astronomical Database|url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=HIP+11915|website=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad|accessdate=16 July 2015|archive-date=2015-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224204836/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=HIP+11915|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該恆星為[[類太陽恆星|類太陽恆星]]，必須以望遠鏡觀測<ref name=eso1529b>{{cite web |title=The star HIP 11915 in the constellation of Cetus |url=http://www.eso.org/public/images/eso1529b/ |publisher=[[欧洲南方天文台|European Southern Observatory]] |date=15 July 2015 |accessdate=17 July 2015 |archive-date=2016-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121011337/https://www.eso.org/public/images/eso1529b/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==行星系統==
HIP 11915周圍有一顆質量和[[木星|木星]]極為接近，並且與母恆星距離和木星與太陽距離幾乎相等的氣體巨行星{{link-en|HIP 11915 b|HIP 11915 b}}環繞。HIP 11915 b 的發現是引人注意的，因為這是首次在太陽系外發現某些狀態與太陽系內行星相近的[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]<ref name="Jupiter's twin spotted">{{cite news|title=Jupiter's twin spotted|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/jupiter-s-twin-spotted-115071600300_1.html|accessdate=16 July 2015|agency=IANS|publisher=business standard|date=July 16, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305195408/http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/jupiter-s-twin-spotted-115071600300_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Jupiter's twin discovered orbiting star similar to our sun">{{cite news|title=Jupiter's twin discovered orbiting star similar to our sun|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/video/news/video-1199401/Jupiters-twin-discovered-orbiting-star-similar-sun.html|accessdate=16 July 2015|agency=daily mail|archive-date=2015-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150913134307/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/video/news/video-1199401/Jupiters-twin-discovered-orbiting-star-similar-sun.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。徑向速度觀測資料也顯示在HIP 11915系統內沒有軌道週期在1000日以內的氣體巨行星存在，這代表在更靠近母恆星處可能有至少一顆類地行星。

HIP 11915 b是由位於[[智利|智利]][[拉西拉天文台|拉西拉天文台]]，[[欧洲南方天文台|欧洲南方天文台]]所屬的[[ESO_3.6米望遠鏡|ESO 3.6米望遠鏡]]搭載儀器[[高精度徑向速度行星搜索器|高精度徑向速度行星搜索器]]發現<ref name="HIP 11915b: Jupiter Twin Found Orbiting Sun-Like Star">{{cite news|title=HIP 11915b: Jupiter Twin Found Orbiting Sun-Like Star|url=http://www.sci-news.com/astronomy/science-hip11915b-jupiter-twin-sun-like-star-03021.html|accessdate=16 July 2015|agency=Sci-News.com|date=Jul 15, 2015|archive-date=2015-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106231907/http://www.sci-news.com/astronomy/science-hip11915b-jupiter-twin-sun-like-star-03021.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Jupiter Look-Alike Discovered Orbiting Sun-Like Star; Could There Be An Earth Twin?">{{cite news|last1=Bora|first1=Kukil|title=Jupiter Look-Alike Discovered Orbiting Sun-Like Star; Could There Be An Earth Twin?|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/jupiter-look-alike-discovered-orbiting-sun-star-could-there-be-earth-twin-2011228|accessdate=16 July 2015|agency=ib times|date=16 July 2015|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924124813/http://www.ibtimes.com/jupiter-look-alike-discovered-orbiting-sun-star-could-there-be-earth-twin-2011228|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[巴西|巴西]][[圣保罗大学|圣保罗大学]]的天文學家若熱·梅蘭德茲（Jorge Meléndez）表示，「在太陽系外搜尋2.0版地球，與完整的2.0版太陽系是天文學上最讓人興奮的其中一件事」<ref name="JupiterTwin">{{cite web|title=Jupiter Twin Discovered Around Solar Twin|url=http://www.eso.org/public/news/eso1529/|website=http://www.eso.org/|accessdate=16 July 2015|archive-date=2015-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224215552/https://www.eso.org/public/news/eso1529/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

